flowchart TD
    E((E)) --> View[View incident log + type breakdown<br/>+ monthly trend chart]
    View --> Act{Action?}

    Act -- "Log new (canEdit)" --> Form[Fill form: incident type<br/>sitio · date · complainant]
    Form --> Photo[Optional: attach photo]
    Form --> Loc[Optional: pick exact location on mini-map]
    Photo --> Gen[Auto-generate case no.]
    Loc --> Gen
    Gen --> Save[Save to incidents<br/>photo to storage]
    Save --> Audit[(audit_logs trigger)]
    Save --> Refresh[Refresh log + charts]

    Act -- "Update status (canEdit)" --> Status[Status dropdown:<br/>Ongoing / Resolved / Escalated / Dismissed]
    Status --> SaveS[Save status] --> Refresh

    Refresh --> R((R))
